<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>About the forum</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet"  type="text/css" href="/main.css" />
</head>

<body>

    <h1 class="page-logo">
        <a href= "/"><%=forumName%>
            <p>!</p>
            <h2>Forum website</h2>
        </a>
    </h1>

    <h2 class="page-title"> About <%=forumName%> <p>!</p></h2>
    <main>
        <div class="about-container">
            <p class="standard-text">Crack It is a forum application built using Node.js, Express, MySQL, and EJS. It allows users to participate in discussions by posting on different topics.</p>
            <br><br>
            <div class="yellow-box">
                <h2>Features</h2>
            
            <div class="main-content">
            <ul>
                <li>Create new topics and posts</li><br>
                <li>Reply to existing posts</li><br>  
                <li>Search posts by title or content</li><br>
                <li>User profiles and topic pages</li><br>
                <li>Uses MySQL database backend</li><br>
            </ul>
            </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="yellow-box">
            <h2>Future Plans</h2>
            
            <div class="main-content">
            <strong><p>Some features we are planning to add in the future:</p></strong>
            
            <ul>
                <li>User registration and login system</li><br>
                <li>Enhanced post formatting using Markdown</li><br>
                <li>Email notifications for replies</li><br>
                <li>Admin dashboard to manage topics and users</li><br>
            </ul>
            </div>
            </div>
            </div>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
